WhatsappLink plugin allows your end user to directly communicate with you using the WhatsApp button.
This plugin support multiple option to change UI for the button.
Some features of the WhatsappLink are listed below:
	-Change Phone Number
	-Fully Responsive
	-Fully Customizable
	-Custom Welcome Message
	-Change Country Code
	-Change the label of the WhatsApp Button
	-Modify button by changing fontsize
	-Change the position of the button
	-Enable/Disable button for the desktop and mobile version
	-Mobile version shows stripe button that make user to interact
	-Remove label and show only icon
	-Option to change the icon for whatsapp button
	-Easy setting page
	-Popup will set vertically center as per the screen size